{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"Well, as Alexander Graham Bell famously said"},{"time":6000,"text":"on his first successful telephone call,"},{"time":9000,"text":"\"Hello, is that Domino's Pizza?\""},{"time":12000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":14000,"text":"I just really want to thank you very much."},{"time":18000,"text":"As another famous man, Jerry Garcia, said,"},{"time":20000,"text":"\"What a strange, long trip.\""},{"time":24000,"text":"And he should have said,"},{"time":26000,"text":"\"What a strange, long trip it's about to become.\""},{"time":29000,"text":"At this very moment, you are viewing my upper half."},{"time":33000,"text":"My lower half is appearing at a different conference"},{"time":36000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":38000,"text":"in a different country."},{"time":42000,"text":"You can, it turns out, be in two places at once."},{"time":47000,"text":"But still, I'm sorry I can't be with you in person."},{"time":50000,"text":"I'll explain at another time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52000,"text":"And though I'm a rock star,"},{"time":54000,"text":"I just want to assure you that none of my wishes will include a hot tub."},{"time":59000,"text":"But what really turns me on about technology"},{"time":62000,"text":"is not just the ability to get more songs on MP3 players."},{"time":67000,"text":"The revolution -- this revolution -- is much bigger than that."},{"time":72000,"text":"I hope, I believe."},{"time":75000,"text":"What turns me on about the digital age,"},{"time":78000,"text":"what excites me personally,"},{"time":80000,"text":"is that you have closed the gap between dreaming and doing."},{"time":87000,"text":"You see, it used to be that if you wanted to make a record of a song,"},{"time":90000,"text":"you needed a studio and a producer."},{"time":95000,"text":"Now, you need a laptop."},{"time":97000,"text":"If you wanted to make a film, you needed a mass of equipment"},{"time":101000,"text":"and a Hollywood budget."},{"time":103000,"text":"Now, you need a camera that fits in your palm,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and a couple of bucks for a blank DVD."},{"time":110000,"text":"Imagination has been decoupled from the old constraints."},{"time":115000,"text":"And that really, really excites me."},{"time":118000,"text":"I'm excited when I glimpse that kind of thinking writ large."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"What I would like to see is idealism decoupled from all constraints."},{"time":131000,"text":"Political, economic, psychological, whatever."},{"time":135000,"text":"The geopolitical world has got a lot to learn from the digital world."},{"time":140000,"text":"From the ease with which you swept away obstacles"},{"time":143000,"text":"that no one knew could even be budged."},{"time":146000,"text":"And that's actually what I'd like to talk about today."},{"time":151000,"text":"First, though, I should probably explain why, and how,"},{"time":156000,"text":"I got to this place."},{"time":160000,"text":"It's a journey that started 20 years ago."},{"time":167000,"text":"You may remember that song, \"We Are the World,\""},{"time":169000,"text":"or, \"Do They Know It's Christmas?\""},{"time":171000,"text":"Band Aid, Live Aid."},{"time":173000,"text":"Another very tall, grizzled rock star, my friend Sir Bob Geldof,"},{"time":178000,"text":"issued a challenge to \"feed the world.\""},{"time":183000,"text":"It was a great moment, and it utterly changed my life."},{"time":188000,"text":"That summer, my wife, Ali, and myself went to Ethiopia."},{"time":194000,"text":"We went on the quiet to see for ourselves what was going on."},{"time":198000,"text":"We lived in Ethiopia for a month, working at an orphanage."},{"time":202000,"text":"The children had a name for me."},{"time":204000,"text":"They called me, \"The girl with the beard.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"Don't ask."},{"time":212000,"text":"Anyway, we found Africa to be a magical place."},{"time":215000,"text":"Big skies, big hearts, big, shining continent."},{"time":219000,"text":"Beautiful, royal people."},{"time":222000,"text":"Anybody who ever gave anything to Africa got a lot more back."},{"time":226000,"text":"Ethiopia didn't just blow my mind; it opened my mind."},{"time":233000,"text":"Anyway, on our last day at this orphanage"},{"time":236000,"text":"a man handed me his baby and said,"},{"time":240000,"text":"\"Would you take my son with you?\""},{"time":246000,"text":"He knew, in Ireland, that his son would live,"},{"time":249000,"text":"and that in Ethiopia, his son would die."},{"time":253000,"text":"It was the middle of that awful famine."},{"time":257000,"text":"Well, I turned him down."},{"time":262000,"text":"And it was a funny kind of sick feeling, but I turned him down."},{"time":269000,"text":"And it's a feeling I can't ever quite forget."},{"time":273000,"text":"And in that moment, I started this journey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"In that moment, I became the worst thing of all:"},{"time":281000,"text":"I became a rock star with a cause. (Laughter)"},{"time":285000,"text":"Except this isn't the cause, is it?"},{"time":290000,"text":"Six-and-a-half thousand Africans dying every single day from AIDS --"},{"time":294000,"text":"a preventable, treatable disease --"},{"time":296000,"text":"for lack of drugs we can get in any pharmacy."},{"time":300000,"text":"That's not a cause. That's an emergency."},{"time":304000,"text":"11 million AIDS orphans in Africa,"},{"time":306000,"text":"20 million by the end of the decade."},{"time":308000,"text":"That's not a cause. That's an emergency."},{"time":311000,"text":"Today, every day, 9,000 more Africans"},{"time":316000,"text":"will catch HIV because of stigmatization and lack of education."},{"time":321000,"text":"That's not a cause. That's an emergency."},{"time":326000,"text":"So what we're talking about here is human rights."},{"time":331000,"text":"The right to live like a human."},{"time":334000,"text":"The right to live, period."},{"time":337000,"text":"And what we're facing in Africa is"},{"time":339000,"text":"an unprecedented threat to human dignity and equality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"The next thing I'd like to be clear about is what this problem is,"},{"time":348000,"text":"and what this problem isn't."},{"time":352000,"text":"Because this is not all about charity."},{"time":355000,"text":"This is about justice. Really."},{"time":359000,"text":"This is not about charity. This is about justice."},{"time":363000,"text":"That's right."},{"time":365000,"text":"And that's too bad, because we're very good at charity."},{"time":368000,"text":"Americans, like Irish people, are good at it."},{"time":372000,"text":"Even the poorest neighborhoods give more than they can afford."},{"time":376000,"text":"We like to give, and we give a lot."},{"time":378000,"text":"Look at the response to the tsunami -- it's inspiring."},{"time":382000,"text":"But justice is a tougher standard than charity."},{"time":387000,"text":"You see, Africa makes a fool of our idea of justice."},{"time":392000,"text":"It makes a farce of our idea of equality."},{"time":395000,"text":"It mocks our pieties. It doubts our concern."},{"time":398000,"text":"It questions our commitment."},{"time":401000,"text":"Because there is no way we can look at what's happening in Africa,"},{"time":405000,"text":"and if we're honest,"},{"time":407000,"text":"conclude that it would ever be allowed to happen anywhere else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"As you heard in the film, anywhere else, not here."},{"time":413000,"text":"Not here, not in America, not in Europe."},{"time":417000,"text":"In fact, a head of state that you're all familiar with"},{"time":422000,"text":"admitted this to me. And it's really true."},{"time":427000,"text":"There is no chance this kind of hemorrhaging of human life"},{"time":431000,"text":"would be accepted anywhere else other than Africa."},{"time":436000,"text":"Africa is a continent in flames."},{"time":440000,"text":"And deep down, if we really accepted that Africans were equal to us,"},{"time":443000,"text":"we would all do more to put the fire out."},{"time":446000,"text":"We're standing around with watering cans,"},{"time":449000,"text":"when what we really need is the fire brigade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452000,"text":"You see, it's not as dramatic as the tsunami."},{"time":458000,"text":"It's crazy, really, when you think about it."},{"time":461000,"text":"Does stuff have to look like an action movie these days"},{"time":464000,"text":"to exist in the front of our brain?"},{"time":467000,"text":"The slow extinguishing of countless lives"},{"time":470000,"text":"is just not dramatic enough, it would appear."},{"time":474000,"text":"Catastrophes that we can avert"},{"time":476000,"text":"are not as interesting as ones we could avert."},{"time":481000,"text":"Funny, that."},{"time":483000,"text":"Anyway, I believe that that kind of thinking"},{"time":486000,"text":"offends the intellectual rigor in this room."},{"time":492000,"text":"Six-and-a-half thousand people dying a day in Africa may be Africa's crisis,"},{"time":497000,"text":"but the fact that it's not on the nightly news,"},{"time":500000,"text":"that we in Europe, or you in America,"},{"time":502000,"text":"are not treating it like an emergency --"},{"time":504000,"text":"I want to argue with you tonight that that's our crisis."},{"time":508000,"text":"I want to argue that though Africa is not the front line in the war against terror,"},{"time":514000,"text":"it could be soon."},{"time":516000,"text":"Every week, religious extremists take another African village."},{"time":521000,"text":"They're attempting to bring order to chaos."},{"time":523000,"text":"Well, why aren't we?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"Poverty breeds despair. We know this."},{"time":528000,"text":"Despair breeds violence. We know this."},{"time":531000,"text":"In turbulent times, isn't it cheaper, and smarter,"},{"time":535000,"text":"to make friends out of potential enemies"},{"time":538000,"text":"than to defend yourself against them later?"},{"time":542000,"text":"\"The war against terror is bound up in the war against poverty.\""},{"time":549000,"text":"And I didn't say that. Colin Powell said that."},{"time":552000,"text":"Now when the military are telling us that this is a war"},{"time":555000,"text":"that cannot be won by military might alone,"},{"time":558000,"text":"maybe we should listen."},{"time":561000,"text":"There's an opportunity here, and it's real."},{"time":564000,"text":"It's not spin. It's not wishful thinking."},{"time":567000,"text":"The problems facing the developing world"},{"time":569000,"text":"afford us in the developed world"},{"time":571000,"text":"a chance to re-describe ourselves to the world."},{"time":577000,"text":"We will not only transform other people's lives,"},{"time":579000,"text":"but we will also transform the way those other lives see us."},{"time":583000,"text":"And that might be smart in these nervous, dangerous times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"Don't you think that on a purely commercial level,"},{"time":593000,"text":"that anti-retroviral drugs are great advertisements"},{"time":597000,"text":"for Western ingenuity and technology?"},{"time":600000,"text":"Doesn't compassion look well on us?"},{"time":602000,"text":"And let's cut the crap for a second."},{"time":606000,"text":"In certain quarters of the world, brand EU, brand USA,"},{"time":612000,"text":"is not at its shiniest."},{"time":616000,"text":"The neon sign is fizzing and cracking."},{"time":619000,"text":"Someone's put a brick through the window."},{"time":622000,"text":"The regional branch managers are getting nervous."},{"time":626000,"text":"Never before have we in the west been so scrutinized."},{"time":630000,"text":"Our values: do we have any?"},{"time":632000,"text":"Our credibility?"},{"time":634000,"text":"These things are under attack around the world."},{"time":636000,"text":"Brand USA could use some polishing."},{"time":641000,"text":"And I say that as a fan, you know?"},{"time":643000,"text":"As a person who buys the products."},{"time":645000,"text":"But think about it."},{"time":647000,"text":"More anti-retrovirals make sense."},{"time":651000,"text":"But that's just the easy part, or ought to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"But equality for Africa --"},{"time":659000,"text":"that's a big, expensive idea."},{"time":663000,"text":"You see, the scale of the suffering numbs us into a kind of indifference."},{"time":667000,"text":"What on earth can we all do about this?"},{"time":672000,"text":"Well, much more than we think."},{"time":674000,"text":"We can't fix every problem, but the ones we can,"},{"time":677000,"text":"I want to argue, we must."},{"time":679000,"text":"And because we can, we must."},{"time":683000,"text":"This is the straight truth, the righteous truth."},{"time":688000,"text":"It is not a theory."},{"time":690000,"text":"The fact is that ours is the first generation"},{"time":693000,"text":"that can look disease and extreme poverty in the eye,"},{"time":697000,"text":"look across the ocean to Africa, and say this, and mean it:"},{"time":701000,"text":"we do not have to stand for this."},{"time":704000,"text":"A whole continent written off -- we do not have to stand for this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":719000,"text":"And let me say this without a trace of irony --"},{"time":725000,"text":"before I back it up to a bunch of ex-hippies."},{"time":728000,"text":"Forget the '60s. We can change the world."},{"time":733000,"text":"I can't; you can't, as individuals; but we can change the world."},{"time":739000,"text":"I really believe that, the people in this room."},{"time":741000,"text":"Look at the Gates Foundation."},{"time":743000,"text":"They've done incredible stuff, unbelievable stuff."},{"time":746000,"text":"But working together, we can actually change the world."},{"time":750000,"text":"We can turn the inevitable outcomes,"},{"time":753000,"text":"and transform the quality of life for millions of lives"},{"time":760000,"text":"who look and feel rather like us, when you're up close."},{"time":766000,"text":"I'm sorry to laugh here, but you do look so different"},{"time":770000,"text":"than you did in Haight-Ashbury in the '60s."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":777000,"text":"But I want to argue that this is the moment that you are designed for."},{"time":783000,"text":"It is the flowering of the seeds you planted"},{"time":786000,"text":"in earlier, headier days."},{"time":790000,"text":"Ideas that you gestated in your youth."},{"time":794000,"text":"This is what excites me."},{"time":796000,"text":"This room was born for this moment,"},{"time":800000,"text":"is really what I want to say to you tonight."},{"time":802000,"text":"Most of you started out wanting to change the world, didn't you?"},{"time":806000,"text":"Most of you did, the digital world."},{"time":809000,"text":"Well, now, actually because of you,"},{"time":812000,"text":"it is possible to change the physical world."},{"time":815000,"text":"It's a fact."},{"time":816000,"text":"Economists confirm it, and they know much more than I do."},{"time":821000,"text":"So why, then, are we not pumping our fists into the air?"},{"time":828000,"text":"Probably because when we admit we can do something about it,"},{"time":832000,"text":"we've got to do something about it."},{"time":836000,"text":"It is a pain in the arse."},{"time":839000,"text":"This equality business is actually a pain in the arse."},{"time":843000,"text":"But for the first time in history, we have the technology;"},{"time":848000,"text":"we have the know-how; we have the cash;"},{"time":850000,"text":"we have the life-saving drugs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"Do we have the will?"},{"time":856000,"text":"I hope this is obvious, but I'm not a hippie."},{"time":862000,"text":"And I'm not really one for the warm, fuzzy feeling."},{"time":865000,"text":"I do not have flowers in my hair."},{"time":868000,"text":"Actually, I come from punk rock."},{"time":871000,"text":"The Clash wore big army boots, not sandals."},{"time":876000,"text":"But I know toughness when I see it."},{"time":879000,"text":"And for all the talk of peace and love on the West Coast,"},{"time":882000,"text":"there was muscle to the movement that started out here."},{"time":889000,"text":"You see, idealism detached from action is just a dream."},{"time":895000,"text":"But idealism allied with pragmatism,"},{"time":899000,"text":"with rolling up your sleeves and making the world bend a bit,"},{"time":902000,"text":"is very exciting. It's very real. It's very strong."},{"time":907000,"text":"And it's very present in a crowd like you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":914000,"text":"Last year at DATA, this organization I helped set up,"},{"time":919000,"text":"we launched a campaign to summon this spirit"},{"time":922000,"text":"in the fight against AIDS and extreme poverty."},{"time":925000,"text":"We're calling it the ONE Campaign."},{"time":928000,"text":"It's based on our belief that the action of one person"},{"time":932000,"text":"can change a lot,"},{"time":934000,"text":"but the actions of many coming together as one"},{"time":938000,"text":"can change the world."},{"time":940000,"text":"Well, we feel that now is the time to prove we're right."},{"time":946000,"text":"There are moments in history when civilization redefines itself."},{"time":951000,"text":"We believe this is one."},{"time":953000,"text":"We believe that this could be the time when the world finally decides"},{"time":957000,"text":"that the wanton loss of life in Africa is just no longer acceptable."},{"time":962000,"text":"This could be the time that we finally get serious"},{"time":965000,"text":"about changing the future for most people who live on planet Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":972000,"text":"Momentum has been building."},{"time":975000,"text":"Lurching a little, but it's building."},{"time":978000,"text":"This year is a test for us all,"},{"time":980000,"text":"especially the leaders of the G8 nations,"},{"time":984000,"text":"who really are on the line here,"},{"time":986000,"text":"with all the world in history watching."},{"time":989000,"text":"I have been, of late, disappointed with the Bush Administration."},{"time":994000,"text":"They started out with such promise on Africa."},{"time":997000,"text":"They made some really great promises,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"and actually have fulfilled a lot of them."},{"time":1003000,"text":"But some of them they haven't."},{"time":1006000,"text":"They don't feel the push from the ground, is the truth."},{"time":1012000,"text":"But my disappointment has much more perspective"},{"time":1016000,"text":"when I talk to American people,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"and I hear their worries about the deficit,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"and the fiscal well being of their country."},{"time":1023000,"text":"I understand that."},{"time":1025000,"text":"But there's much more push from the ground than you'd think,"},{"time":1030000,"text":"if we got organized."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1032000,"text":"What I try to communicate, and you can help me if you agree,"},{"time":1036000,"text":"is that aid for Africa is just great value for money"},{"time":1040000,"text":"at a time when America really needs it."},{"time":1043000,"text":"Putting it in the crassest possible terms,"},{"time":1046000,"text":"the investment reaps huge returns."},{"time":1050000,"text":"Not only in lives saved, but in goodwill, stability"},{"time":1054000,"text":"and security that we'll gain."},{"time":1060000,"text":"So this is what I hope that you will do, if I could be so bold,"},{"time":1064000,"text":"and not have it deducted from my number of wishes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1069000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072000,"text":"What I hope is that beyond individual merciful acts,"},{"time":1078000,"text":"that you will tell the politicians to do right by Africa,"},{"time":1083000,"text":"by America and by the world."},{"time":1086000,"text":"Give them permission, if you like,"},{"time":1088000,"text":"to spend their political capital and your financial capital,"},{"time":1093000,"text":"your national purse on saving the lives of millions of people."},{"time":1096000,"text":"That's really what I would like you to do."},{"time":1100000,"text":"Because we also need your intellectual capital:"},{"time":1104000,"text":"your ideas, your skills, your ingenuity."},{"time":1108000,"text":"And you, at this conference, are in a unique position."},{"time":1112000,"text":"Some of the technologies we've been talking about, you invented them,"},{"time":1115000,"text":"or at least revolutionized the way that they're used."},{"time":1119000,"text":"Together you have changed the zeitgeist from analog to digital,"},{"time":1123000,"text":"and pushed the boundaries."},{"time":1127000,"text":"And we'd like you to give us that energy."},{"time":1132000,"text":"Give us that kind of dreaming, that kind of doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1135000,"text":"As I say, there're two things on the line here."},{"time":1137000,"text":"There's the continent Africa."},{"time":1141000,"text":"But there's also our sense of ourselves."},{"time":1144000,"text":"People are starting to figure this out."},{"time":1146000,"text":"Movements are springing up."},{"time":1147000,"text":"Artists, politicians, pop stars, priests, CEOs,"},{"time":1150000,"text":"NGOs, mothers' unions, student unions."},{"time":1155000,"text":"A lot of people are getting together, and working"},{"time":1157000,"text":"under this umbrella I told you about earlier, the ONE Campaign."},{"time":1162000,"text":"I think they just have one idea in their mind,"},{"time":1169000,"text":"which is, where you live in the world"},{"time":1173000,"text":"should not determine whether you live in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1178000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1182000,"text":"History, like God, is watching what we do."},{"time":1187000,"text":"When the history books get written,"},{"time":1189000,"text":"I think our age will be remembered for three things."},{"time":1193000,"text":"Really, it's just three things this whole age will be remembered for."},{"time":1197000,"text":"The digital revolution, yes."},{"time":1200000,"text":"The war against terror, yes."},{"time":1203000,"text":"And what we did or did not do to put out the fires in Africa."},{"time":1210000,"text":"Some say we can't afford to. I say we can't afford not to."},{"time":1218000,"text":"Thank you, thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1220000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1227000,"text":"Okay, my three wishes."},{"time":1230000,"text":"The ones that TED has offered to grant."},{"time":1236000,"text":"You see, if this is true, and I believe it is,"},{"time":1238000,"text":"that the digital world you all created has uncoupled"},{"time":1244000,"text":"the creative imagination from the physical constraints of matter,"},{"time":1250000,"text":"this should be a piece of piss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1252000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1256000,"text":"I should add that this started out as a much longer list of wishes."},{"time":1259000,"text":"Most of them impossible, some of them impractical"},{"time":1261000,"text":"and one or two of them certainly immoral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1265000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1269000,"text":"This business, it gets to be addictive, you know what I mean,"},{"time":1273000,"text":"when somebody else is picking up the tab."},{"time":1276000,"text":"Anyway, here's number one."},{"time":1279000,"text":"I wish for you to help build a social movement"},{"time":1286000,"text":"of more than one million American activists for Africa."},{"time":1293000,"text":"That is my first wish."},{"time":1295000,"text":"I believe it's possible."},{"time":1297000,"text":"A few minutes ago, I talked about all the citizens' campaigns that are springing up."},{"time":1302000,"text":"You know, there's lots out there."},{"time":1304000,"text":"And with this one campaign as our umbrella,"},{"time":1307000,"text":"my organization, DATA, and other groups,"},{"time":1310000,"text":"have been tapping into the energy and the enthusiasm"},{"time":1314000,"text":"that's out there from Hollywood into the heartland of America."},{"time":1318000,"text":"We know there's more than enough energy to power this movement."},{"time":1322000,"text":"We just need your help in making it happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1326000,"text":"We want all of you here, church America, corporate America,"},{"time":1328000,"text":"Microsoft America, Apple America, Coke America,"},{"time":1331000,"text":"Pepsi America, nerd America, noisy America."},{"time":1334000,"text":"We can't afford to be cool and sit this one out."},{"time":1338000,"text":"I do believe if we build a movement that's one million Americans strong,"},{"time":1343000,"text":"we're not going to be denied."},{"time":1346000,"text":"We will have the ear of Congress."},{"time":1351000,"text":"We'll be the first page in Condi Rice's briefing book,"},{"time":1354000,"text":"and right into the Oval Office."},{"time":1357000,"text":"If there's one million Americans -- and I really know this --"},{"time":1360000,"text":"who are ready to make phone calls,"},{"time":1362000,"text":"who are ready to be on email,"},{"time":1364000,"text":"I am absolutely sure that we can actually change"},{"time":1368000,"text":"the course of history, literally, for the continent of Africa."},{"time":1374000,"text":"Anyway, so I'd like your help in getting that signed up."},{"time":1378000,"text":"I know John Gage and Sun Microsystems are already on board for this,"},{"time":1382000,"text":"but there's lots of you we'd like to talk to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1385000,"text":"Right, my second wish, number two."},{"time":1393000,"text":"I would like one media hit for every person on the planet"},{"time":1398000,"text":"who is living on less than one dollar a day."},{"time":1403000,"text":"That's one billion media hits."},{"time":1406000,"text":"Could be on Google, could be on AOL."},{"time":1409000,"text":"Steve Case, Larry, Sergey -- they've done a lot already."},{"time":1415000,"text":"It could be NBC. It could be ABC."},{"time":1417000,"text":"Actually we're talking to ABC today about the Oscars."},{"time":1420000,"text":"We have a film, produced by Jon Kamen at Radical Media."},{"time":1426000,"text":"But you know, we want, we need some airtime for our ideas."},{"time":1430000,"text":"We need to get the math; we need to get the statistics out to the American people."},{"time":1434000,"text":"I really believe that old Truman line,"},{"time":1437000,"text":"that if you give the American people the facts,"},{"time":1440000,"text":"they'll do the right thing."},{"time":1442000,"text":"And, the other thing that's important is that this is not Sally Struthers."},{"time":1446000,"text":"This has to be described as an adventure, not a burden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1451000,"text":"(Video): One by one they step forward,"},{"time":1453000,"text":"a nurse, a teacher, a homemaker,"},{"time":1455000,"text":"and lives are saved."},{"time":1457000,"text":"The problem is enormous."},{"time":1459000,"text":"Every three seconds one person dies."},{"time":1462000,"text":"Another three seconds, one more."},{"time":1465000,"text":"The situation is so desperate in parts of Africa,"},{"time":1468000,"text":"Asia, even America,"},{"time":1470000,"text":"that aid groups, just as they did for the tsunami,"},{"time":1473000,"text":"are uniting as one, acting as one."},{"time":1477000,"text":"We can beat extreme poverty, starvation, AIDS."},{"time":1481000,"text":"But we need your help."},{"time":1483000,"text":"One more person, letter, voice"},{"time":1485000,"text":"will mean the difference between life and death"},{"time":1488000,"text":"for millions of people."},{"time":1491000,"text":"Please join us by working together."},{"time":1493000,"text":"Americans have an unprecedented opportunity."},{"time":1496000,"text":"We can make history."},{"time":1498000,"text":"We can start to make poverty history."},{"time":1501000,"text":"One, by one, by one."},{"time":1503000,"text":"Please visit ONE at this address."},{"time":1506000,"text":"We're not asking for your money. We're asking for your voice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1511000,"text":"Bono: All right. I wish for TED to truly show the power of information,"},{"time":1519000,"text":"its power to rewrite the rules and transform lives,"},{"time":1524000,"text":"by connecting every hospital, health clinic and school"},{"time":1530000,"text":"in one African country."},{"time":1534000,"text":"And I would like it to be Ethiopia."},{"time":1537000,"text":"I believe we can connect every school in Ethiopia,"},{"time":1541000,"text":"every health clinic, every hospital --"},{"time":1544000,"text":"we can connect to the Internet."},{"time":1547000,"text":"That is my wish, my third wish."},{"time":1549000,"text":"I think it's possible."},{"time":1550000,"text":"I think we have the money and brains in the room to do that."},{"time":1553000,"text":"And that would be a mind-blowing wish to come true."},{"time":1559000,"text":"I've been to Ethiopia, as I said earlier."},{"time":1562000,"text":"It's actually where it all started for me."},{"time":1569000,"text":"The idea that the Internet, which changed all of our lives,"},{"time":1573000,"text":"can transform a country -- and a continent"},{"time":1577000,"text":"that has hardly made it to analog, let alone digital -- blows my mind."},{"time":1584000,"text":"But it didn't start out that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1587000,"text":"The first long-distance line from Boston to New York"},{"time":1590000,"text":"was used in 1885 on the phone."},{"time":1596000,"text":"It was just nine years later that Addis Ababa"},{"time":1600000,"text":"was connected by phone to Harare, which is 500 kilometers away."},{"time":1607000,"text":"Since then, not that much has changed."},{"time":1610000,"text":"The average waiting time to get a landline in Ethiopia"},{"time":1614000,"text":"is actually about seven or eight years."},{"time":1618000,"text":"But wireless technology wasn't dreamt up then."},{"time":1624000,"text":"Anyway, I'm Irish, and as you can see,"},{"time":1626000,"text":"I know how important talking is."},{"time":1630000,"text":"Communication is very important for Ethiopia -- will transform the country."},{"time":1634000,"text":"Nurses getting better training,"},{"time":1636000,"text":"pharmacists being able to order supplies,"},{"time":1638000,"text":"doctors sharing their expertise in all aspects of medicine."},{"time":1643000,"text":"It's a very, very good idea to get them wired."},{"time":1647000,"text":"And that is my third and final wish for you at the TED conference."},{"time":1651000,"text":"Thank you very much once again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1653000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}